description:
The game features a system similar to that of God of War and Devil May Cry, even having some of the same controls and style of attacks. Combos are done with bare hands and with the Demonic chain. The overall mood, setting and visual style are very much the same as those in the first installment of Devil May Cry. When on the Hellcycle, Ghost Rider is still capable of performing some of the same chain attacks, and can shoot hellfire.

This is a PSP emulation using the latest version of PPSSPP, which is Xbox360 controller compatible.

Recommended System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher.

nVidia GeForce GT 610 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.

2 Gig of ram or more.

Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.

